# Expenso Tracker - Environment Variables

# SMTP Configuration (Optional)
# Fill these in to send password reset codes to real mailboxes.
# If left empty, Expenso Tracker automatically falls back to an Ethereal virtual mailbox, 
# displaying a click-to-open sandbox inbox link directly in the app UI for testing.

# SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_USER=your-email@gmail.com
# SMTP_PASS=your-gmail-app-password
